text:
Aur be kaisa hai.... Kya likhe tere bare me, naam hi kaafi hai. Perfect roommate to nhi hi tha tu. Sat, Sun breakfast ke liye aadhi neend me jaata tha tu mess. Cricket, wing football khena, dusro ke room pe sath jaake bakaiti krne me bhut maja aata tha. Kudos, tune rote rote placement lagwa hi liya. 
Best of luck for future, and roz naha liya kr ab.
author: Aniket  Raj

text:
Aur batao Aaarchies, kaisa hai... Tere gusse me nikla hua innovative gaali, tera bina baat ka bak****i bahut maja aata tha sunne me. Waise guitar mast bajata hai tu, humlog sabhi me. Tera quantum physics me interest dekh ke mujhe civil chhod dene ka man krta tha.... Kaafi memories hai hamari bhi - Saath me first year ke courses, fest enjoy krna, psych, cricket and ha... basket ball me wrong basket krne wala akela banda tha tu.... 
Khush reh hamesha and achieve all your dreams.

text:
Aur haathi, tere baare me kya hi likhe. Bak**** launda, daring, dassa boi, fitness freak sab tha tu....but chutiya bhi tha. Bina koi reason ke tere room ki gate pe laat marne me alag maja aata tha. Tere saath bhi kaafi memories rhi, projects, assignment krna, fest me maje krna, gyan pelna, sab unforgettable hai. Tere se bahut kuch sikha bhi maine.

text:
Aur bro kaisa hai.... Tere saath bhi kaafi memories rhe. Tere room pe aake khub pareshan kiya maine. Kitna bhi tension rhta, tu hamesha haste rhta, saara R***i Rona chhupa ke. Summers me swimming krna, cricket, basket ball, wing football khelna, exams ke baad puri raat mafia khelne ka alag hi maja tha. Saath me hamne fest me bhi kaafi enjoy kiya.... Unforgettable memories hai yaar.
Always keep smiling and good luck for your future, and guitar bhi bajate rho.
